---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Privacy Policy" description="Privacy Policy for Are You a Heretic?.">
  <div data-pagefind-ignore="all" class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 py-16 prose-heresy">
    <h1 class="font-display text-4xl font-bold text-charcoal mb-6">Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p class="text-charcoal/70">Last updated: 2026-03-30</p>

    <p class="text-charcoal/80 mt-6">
      Are You a Heretic? is operated by Probably Theology. This policy explains what data is collected and how it is used.
    </p>

    <h2 class="font-display text-2xl font-bold text-charcoal mt-8 mb-3">What we collect</h2>
    <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-charcoal/80 space-y-2">
      <li>Newsletter signups submitted through the embedded Kit form (email and any details you provide).</li>
      <li>Contact form submissions sent via Web3Forms (name, email, message, and anti-spam metadata).</li>
      <li>Basic analytics and advertising-related data (for example page views, device/browser data, and ad signals).</li>
      <li>A local browser preference for dismissing the work-in-progress banner.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2 class="font-display text-2xl font-bold text-charcoal mt-8 mb-3">Newsletter consent</h2>
    <p class="text-charcoal/80">
      Newsletter signup on this site subscribes you to the Probably Theology newsletter. Emails may include theology content, updates about related projects, and OpenScripture launch updates. You can unsubscribe at any time using the link in any newsletter email.
    </p>

    <h2 class="font-display text-2xl font-bold text-charcoal mt-8 mb-3">How data is used</h2>
    <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-charcoal/80 space-y-2">
      <li>To deliver requested newsletter emails.</li>
      <li>To respond to messages sent through the contact form.</li>
      <li>To improve site performance, content, and reliability.</li>
      <li>To support site operations, including advertising and abuse prevention.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2 class="font-display text-2xl font-bold text-charcoal mt-8 mb-3">Third-party services</h2>
    <p class="text-charcoal/80">
      This site uses Kit (ConvertKit), Web3Forms, Google Analytics, and Google AdSense. These services process data under their own privacy policies.
    </p>

    <h2 class="font-display text-2xl font-bold text-charcoal mt-8 mb-3">Your choices</h2>
    <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-charcoal/80 space-y-2">
      <li>Unsubscribe from newsletter emails at any time.</li>
      <li>Do not submit the contact form if you do not want your message data processed.</li>
      <li>Use browser controls to manage cookies and local storage.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2 class="font-display text-2xl font-bold text-charcoal mt-8 mb-3">Contact</h2>
    <p class="text-charcoal/80">
      Questions about privacy: <a class="text-crimson underline" href="mailto:openscriptureapp@gmail.com">openscriptureapp@gmail.com</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
